<h2 id="register-and-login-with-phone-number">Register and login with phone number</h2>

<h3 id="register">Register:</h3>

<p>Users can choose to register with their email and password, or to choose to register with their phone number.</p>

<ol>
  <li>A user visits your site and choose to register.</li>
  <li>We send them an SMS with a code.</li>
  <li>They enter the code, if itâ€™s valid.</li>
  <li>We ask them for name and email.</li>
  <li>User is successfully registered!</li>
</ol>

<h3 id="login">Login:</h3>

<ol>
  <li>Registered user visits your site and wants to login.</li>
  <li>He/She chooses to login with a phone number and enters his/her number.</li>
  <li>If the number is valid and a profile account with that phone number is found, we send them a code.</li>
  <li>The user enters the code.</li>
  <li>If the code is valid,  the user is successfully logged in!</li>
</ol>
